|Admin|
start
:① Invite organizer
(set organizer club in Admin page);

|Organizer|
:② Create meet structure
(Create Pool/Beach — or import .lxf);
:③ Send invitations
→ coaches receive PIN by email;

|Coaches|
:④ Log in
Register athletes
Adjust entry times;

|Organizer|
:⑤ Closure date passes
→ Send Stripe invoices;
:⑥ Export registrations (.lxf);

|SauvetageMeet|
:Import · Seed heats
Run competition
Record times
Export results (.lxf);

|Organizer|
:⑦ Import results (.lxf)
**Meet closed**;

note right
  • Results archived (historical)
  • Current meet reset
  • All PINs regenerated
  • Organizer logged out
end note

|Admin|
:↩ Back to step ①;
stop

